> "WHAT ARE WE DOING?????"said the male to a Maurader 
> while he followed him

Marauder said nothing for a long while, instead just continuing to fly. Ground slipped quietly and quickly underneath them, as they flew southward. Marauder's boosters lit the skies for a moment as if ignoring the comment from the minions behind him, but then at last he slowed as they came out over the open waters of the Pacific Oceans. 

"What do your memory banks tell you of the humans will one day call the Indonesian islands, more specifically Bali?" Marauder finally said as he banked into a more westerly direction, the ancient open oceans seeming to beckon to the minions with sparkling blue waters as they flew.

(TAG: Darkfate)

"Do you not remember anything of a place called Demon swamp?" Marauder chuckled evilly as he flew onward. "Indeed, how else to construct MY army, then with those who can do it so easily: the INSECTICONS!"

(TAG: Darkfate)

Preston
